value: Early in the morning, late at night...\nOne of them sneaks off to— Hm?
To eat a cookie?! That's not fair!\nThat makes things a little awkward...
To train alone?! A great idea!\nTwo can train at night, you know...
The rising sun paints the sky beautiful.\nIt's a joyous gift for nighttime training!
$aFoes grant 5x SP for the next $a0,\nand then 2x SP thereafter! (Only highest\nvalue applied. Does not stack.)
